==Damage Formulas==

===Black Magic===
<pre>
Damage = (Base Power × (Intelligence / 4 + 1)) × (100 - Target MagDef) / 100
</pre>

===Elemental Weakness===
<pre>
If target weak to element: Damage × 2
If target absorbs element: Damage heals instead
If target nullifies element: Damage = 0
</pre>

===Summon Magic===
<pre>
Damage = (Summon Power × (Intelligence / 2 + 1)) × (100 - Target MagDef) / 100
</pre>

